videos.description: Diontae Johnson snags a 27-yard touchdown pass from Logan Woodside.
videos.headline: Toledo's Johnson makes leaping TD grab

videos.description: Terry Swanson pounds in a 2-yard touchdown to extend Toledo's lead.
videos.headline: Swanson powers in for Toledo TD

videos.description: Logan Woodside lobs it up to Diontae Johnson who makes a one-handed catch in the corner of the end zone.
videos.headline: Johnson makes sweet one-handed TD snag for Toledo

videos.description: Trevon Mathis jumps in front of the receiver to pick off Thomas Woodson's pass.
videos.headline: Toledo's Mathis picks off Woodson

videos.description: Ulysees Gilbert III intercepts Logan Woodside's pass and returns it 25 yards.
videos.headline: Gilbert grabs INT for Akron

videos.description: Logan Woodside hits Jon'Vea Johnson down the sidlene for a 27-yard Toledo touchdown.
videos.headline: Johnson reels in 27-yard TD

videos.description: Toledo head coach Jason Candle says his quarterback Logan Woodside has played like a fifth-year player in the first half against Akron.
videos.headline: Candle proud of quarterback play

videos.description: Logan Woodside throws to Shakif Seymour who runs it into the end zone for a 12-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Woodside hits Seymour for Toledo TD

videos.description: Manny Morgan scores Akron's first touchdown with a 7-yard run up the middle.
videos.headline: Morgan puts Akron on the board

videos.description: Kato Nelson makes a perfect pass to Austin Wolf who makes a great catch for a 29-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Akron's Wolf makes diving TD catch

videos.description: Olasunkanmi Adeniyi sacks Kato Nelson who fumbles and it's recovered by Marquise Moore for Toledo.
videos.headline: Adeniyi's strip-sack gives Toledo the ball

videos.description: Terry Swanson takes the hand off 54 yards for a Toledo touchdown.
videos.headline: Swanson breaks off 54-yard TD
